From: Puranjay Mohan <puranjay@kernel.org>
Date: Thu, 24 Jul 2025 12:02:55 +0000
Subject: selftests/bpf: Enable private stack tests for arm64
Patch-mainline: v6.17-rc1
Git-commit: e9f545d0d336b37ece594a0bfd8d2d13ccbed6ab
